<p><strong>唐·费雷罗之谲——太刀（Don Ferreiro's Lie-Katana）</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/impslayer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(557469); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=557469&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608707615" alt="Impslayer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=557469)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/impslayer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(557469); return false;">Impslayer</a></span><br />
<strong>原文：</strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/don-ferreiros-lie-katana">Don Ferreiro's Lie-Katana</a><br />
